                     <interp inst="t18270531-129-person804" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a butcher. I went and found this money in the dirt.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182705310068"></xptr>MRS. SMITH. I had been to the till two minutes before, and saw the money safe; I can swear to him by the silk handkerchief round his neck.</p>
